At IWC Schaffhausen, we invite you to celebrate the national day in a very special way. Get enchanted by the delicate melody of our timepieces revisiting the Swiss hymn with finesse and pride, conducted by none other than IWC Master Watchmaker, Mr. Kurt Klaus. 
@kurt.klaus

#IWCPilot #IWCON

node.text:
Congratulations to brand ambassador @LewisHamilton on being awarded the Laureus Athlete Advocate of the Year Award at the 22nd edition of the Laureus World Sports Awards.
“A huge thank you to the Laureus World Sports Academy for presenting me with this incredible Award. This past year has been incredibly difficult for so many, but it has also been heartening to see the power of our collective voices spark new conversations and change. The global rising to address the longstanding issue of systemic racism and inequality in our society has been monumental, but we must continue to fight. We must all see ourselves as responsible for making positive change in our world, and hold ourselves accountable, so that the promises of last year turn in to action. I truly believe that together, we will get there, and so I stand with you as we push forwards.” #IWCLaureus #LewisHamilton

node.text:
Golden sun, sea breeze. Escape to the coast this summer with the elegant #IWCPortofino Automatic 37 (Ref. IW458107), with leather strap by @santoniofficial.
#IWCWatches  #SantoniSS21 #SummerEscape @giuseppesantoniofficial

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by IWC Schaffhausen on July 26, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
The Pilot’s Watch Chronograph 41 (Ref. IW388102) shows itself in a new light: athletic and bold with its versatile design. Featuring an ergonomic 41-millimetre case size and powered by the IWC-manufactured 69385 calibre, this model pays tribute to its origins as a key historical navigational instrument for pilots.
#IWCON #IWCPilot

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by IWC Schaffhausen on July 24, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
Stunning and timeless, the Big Pilot’s Watch 43 (Ref. IW329304) is legendary for its elegance on all occasions. This icon comes with a blue or black dial and offers our EasX-CHANGE system to easily switch the strap from stainless steel, calfskin or rubber to better fit with each style. 
#IWCON #IWCPilot

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by IWC Schaffhausen on July 22, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
The Pilot’s Watch Chronograph 41 (Ref. IW388103) never fails to impress with its flamboyant and contemporary green dial, rhodium-plated hands and brown calfskin strap. This timeless masterpiece showcases a robust and precise chronograph movement with a column wheel observable through the sapphire glass back. 
#IWCON #IWCPilot

All watch and coffee enthusiasts, ATTENTION! Presenting the world's very first IWC official cafe, “BIG PILOT BAR BY IWC & CENTER COFFEE” located on the 5th floor of Lotte Main Department Store in Seoul, Korea. Collaborating with Center Coffee, you can expect high quality special blends and coffee drinks. Do drop by this amazing and chic place where you can experience IWC in a new way!
#IWCBigPilot #BigPilotBar
